      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a restoration project or a source for spare parts. The engine is currently non-operational due to a significant internal failure, and the transmission has been slipping for some time. Externally, the body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with faded paint and several noticeable dents. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. While it is a complete car, it will require a trailer for transport and a substantial investment to return to the road.",
