      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It's honestly in pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-tucked and spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without that dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
