    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional FD3S chassis featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains perfect factory tolerances with optimal compression across all rotor faces and no evidence of thermal degradation in the complex vacuum solenoid rack. The drivetrain is anchored by a rigid power-plant frame (PPF) and a Torsen limited-slip differential, delivering power through a precise five-speed longitudinal gearbox. Suspension geometry remains true to its original double-wishbone design, providing unparalleled feedback and a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. This is a mechanically transparent, collector-grade specimen with zero modifications to the induction system or apex seal integrity.",
